{"tid":1899193,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新007 3-4  無恐不入 特務大臨演","createTime":"2020-02-26T12:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T20:30:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41607b57b066f5b04ab5ba2416f67c135b494866","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=b2141dbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=242b5027\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=49104bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/nintchdbpict000345729494.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=882&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fnintchdbpict000345729494.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D882%26quality%3D100&h=737c1171&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://theinvasionmovies.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/theinvasion721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinvasionmovies.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Ftheinvasion721.jpg&h=fda5305e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cb/The_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcb%2FThe_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg&h=064c27d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cb/The_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcb%2FThe_Brothers_Grimsby_Poster.jpg&h=064c27d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.軍情六處（MI6）在伊斯坦堡的秘密據點突然遭人攻擊，軍情六處主管M夫人立刻派遣代號007的詹姆士&middot;龐德前去查看。龐德到達後發現據點的特工已全部陣亡，而軍情六處最重要的臥底特工名單的硬盤也被拿走。龐德出去後遇到前來支援的女特工伊芙，兩人開著吉普追趕開奧迪逃跑的刺客，刺客在走投無路下跳上火車，龐德則是跳上火車與刺客進行肉搏。伊芙在M的命令下拿狙擊槍開了一槍，但發出去的子彈卻意外打到龐德，刺客拿著硬盤揚長而去，龐德掉入河中而從此下落不明..<br />\n<br />\n2.M女士臨終前給詹姆士&middot;龐德留下了一個非官方的命令，讓龐德去墨西哥執行任務。在任務中，龐德殺死了兩名安排去炸毀一座體育館的男子。在爆炸和倒塌聲中，龐德前去追逐在爆炸中逃脫的馬可&middot;斯奇拉，但卻登上斯奇拉逃跑用的直升機。龐德立馬衝上去將斯奇拉和飛行員拋出直升機，並遵照命令偷走了斯奇拉的章魚戒指..<br />\n<br />\n3.一艘發射沒多久的太空梭突然在空中解體，碎片掉落在美國德州到華盛頓州之間；這看似意外的太空梭的解體事故背後卻似乎隱藏者一個極大的陰謀。許多民眾在好奇的情況下去觸碰這些太空梭的碎片，甚至有人把撿到的太空梭碎片拿到eBay上面去賣，有一位名叫塔克（傑瑞米&middot;諾森飾演）的民眾也因此不小心被碎片割傷。而塔克在當天睡覺眼球快速轉動週期過後被細菌改變了其身體結構，隔天就變成被細菌完全控制的人..<br />\n<br />\n4.影片講述一名英國高級特工和一個足球流氓聯手完成任務的故事。高級間諜（馬克&middot;斯特朗飾）為了完成一項任務，他不得不同自己的足球流氓哥哥（薩莎&middot;拜倫&middot;科恩飾）攜手。 28年間，諾比一直在苦苦尋找他的弟弟。<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=57c550b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e1fc2a0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66f67127de838b875a73cfb1e7e3cd4b40a61ed","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582f461fdda82be1ea60b570ca98912184b15825","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a99d718a9363106d02a74cc7555352faeedd8ae","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1945c987012d42f2ad5917724b27711172746f76","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T18:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3490fbe26d609a170ff8deeda439a46e18705f93","tid":1899193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20: